Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對秀樹而言，特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.41,0:01:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹的…只屬於秀樹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.82,0:01:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個人不是小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生跟以前一樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.39,0:02:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不得不有所行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.37,0:02:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不有所行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.32,0:02:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.73,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.06,0:02:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.43,0:02:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#20         小ちぃ，追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺先生打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔打來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.42,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次寄圖片來的帳號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛又寄來一封郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經寄到絲茉茉那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打開看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的郵件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次的圖片跟上次不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道代表什麼意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我得找小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也會繼續找小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之你先看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能成為\N找到小ちぃ的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟解壓縮檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是送圖片的那傢伙\N綁架小ちぃ的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是\N小ちぃ受苦的照片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳就跟屋子裡的\N所有電腦連線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些線路就像緞帶一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緞帶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常適合妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.39,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓那個叫M的傢伙\N特地在BBS上提到的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼特別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該不會讓妳單獨出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以本來想說沒機會遇見妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.61,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到跟M所描述的\N一模一樣的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會出現在書店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來真的不了解妳的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連接端子並不特殊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的內部是不是特製的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ？特別？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是平常那種跟小ちぃ很像的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要寄這個過來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉\N妳知道這是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.55,0:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是附加圖片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逼她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉是攜帶型  的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法回答太抽象的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟本須和處得好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然回來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.91,0:05:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟多香子說了電話中的事之後\N她就很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和對什麼事情都很認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定非常煩惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去幫他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比一個人更容易想出好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到你的電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你還是很擔心是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的確可以消除記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我會記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對方不是生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對方不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就無法當作沒發生過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是很擔心小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趕快去找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，讓我看看妳的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，這張圖片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的電腦失蹤有關嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連這是什麼圖片都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會不會是地圖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這應該是\N導航系統上顯示的地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是手機或是汽車衛星導航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼寄這種東西過來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡的地圖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用電腦查就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用絲茉茉能查到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是比較花時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還是拜託國分寺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個圖片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.39,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰寄來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.36,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有之前寄來的這張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道圖片是誰寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.02,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能做的只有繪畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.53,0:08:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫下小ちぃ在成為小ちぃ之前\N所失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及希望妳未來能找到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.61,0:08:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳能找到屬於妳的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是地圖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不確定是哪裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊來查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，看看這張圖是指哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用區域網路\N與其他電腦一起搜尋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的圖片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不確定是誰寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.71,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想這地圖應該與小ちぃ有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是小ちぃ的所在地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟圖片上地圖相符的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本全國共有12568處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12568處？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這如果是地圖\N也太粗略了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東京市內呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有23處的話\N應該就有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.15,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛檢查過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自製機網站的瀏覽記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那邊有吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那個IP查看\N是來自哪個橋接器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些橋接器當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有跟那23處重疊的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用那個IP連線的人的暱稱是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蜓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才問那是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫蜻蜓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能知道小ちぃ在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有某種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我腦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是主人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是我所熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IP位址跟地圖重疊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走到這地方花不了十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ就在這麼近的地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.11,0:11:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蜓有20台以上的自製機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.38,0:11:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那是間能放得下\N超過20台電腦的大房子囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是每間房子都很大耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我記得\N為了避免那些電腦被偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有跟保全公司簽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在BBS上有寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找貼著保全公司貼紙的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都超過一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用上我家裡電腦的全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還解不開保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是再一下子就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我為了妳而特別寫的程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管妳怎麼抗拒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它都會侵入妳的裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只能乖乖的接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們兩個\N為何會這麼清楚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個叫蜻蜓的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他算是比較引人注意的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使在網站上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引人注意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是胡亂找人吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也常常找上M
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的暱稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在網路上發表文章時使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,類似筆名之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這裡，可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然是特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定妳真的是Chobits系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.53,0:13:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到另一間屋子看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.29,0:14:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊就離開地圖的範圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡可以進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，絲茉茉沒反應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斷訊了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，再撥一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到…聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.07,0:14:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我熟悉的人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最熟悉的人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ只要一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有只屬於我的人可以碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有只屬於我的人可以進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉變得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是小ちぃ做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹最重要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是“那個”\N還是對“人”而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ或許就不必失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.03,0:16:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意識突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀…樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…小ちぃ吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ就是小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為秀樹替我取的\N所以叫小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹來找我\N我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像突然失去了意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是蜻蜓對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對小ちぃ做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是想調查一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就擅自帶她回來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己跟我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己跟你來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，她跟著我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有點奇怪對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人說過是綁架回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.10,0:18:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是對主人不利的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是主人你自己這樣設計的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙說是綁架的那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有錄影下來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時要請妳跟我們一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你所作所為的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.18,0:18:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都記錄在這孩子裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓你隨便消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓你誣賴我\N說我偷走她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著絲茉茉說是交給我們保管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為戴特太可愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差點從這裡掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼傻話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到她了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，戴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再多觀察一下狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後就沒張開過眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然盡快帶她回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻像是變了個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些也是小ちぃ做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話，那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.71,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是小ちぃ做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說小ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是Chobits嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變密碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再說一次密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.46,0:20:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平假、片假、英文、數字等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請一個一個字講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就說不是了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事提到密碼是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.44,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會有人聽見，請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有反應呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於Chobits這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人檢查妳的性能時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的樣子變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時想過妳或許是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的Chobits系列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許只是單純的都市傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來做早操吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要做啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.01,0:21:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家人究竟是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.99,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先通知植田店長\N已經找到小ちぃ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有得去付這個的錢才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ被綁架的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿著這個走了對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本畫冊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很像在說我和小ちぃ的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰，為了什麼而畫的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.69,0:22:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ能回來真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.70,0:22:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.17,0:22:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.11,0:22:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.29,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.50,0:23:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.05,0:23:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.42,0:23:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.46,0:23:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.14,0:23:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，什麼是回憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.43,0:23:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.06,0:23:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愉快或是快樂的事之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包含了所有的事情\N留在心中的重要東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.90,0:23:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過並不像資料一樣\N可以輕易替換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.34,0:23:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小ちぃ跟秀樹也有回憶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.54,0:23:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「小ちぃ，回答」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.58,0:24:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹和小ちぃ的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.35,0:24:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能輕易替換的東西…嗎
